Trade/Device Name(s): Dimension Vista™ System Total Triiodothyronine Calibrator (T3 CAL - KC250)
Dimension Vista™ Total Triiodothyronine Calibrator (T3 CAL, KC250)
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Dimension Vista System Total Triiodothyronine Calibrator (T3 CAL - KC250) for use in calibrating T3 assays on the Dimension Vista System.
Indications for Use Summary: In vitro diagnostic product for the calibration of Total Triiodothyronine (T3) method on the Dimension Vista System.
